{"tid":2320110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"食安中心呼籲市民不要食用兩款意大利進口芝麻油","createTime":"2020-12-10T14:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T18:02:18.000Z","uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b031fcd3f22759d62882752639c9a2aebce06b22","tid":2320110,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564661-20201210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564661-20201210.htm&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=c1edeba5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1564661-20201210.htm&h=621b2f45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1564661-20201210.htm</a><br />\n食物安全中心呼籲市民不要食用兩款意大利進口芝麻油，有關產品被驗出含有可能致癌的環氧乙烷。 <br />\n<br />\n兩款產品分別是Clearspring 的Organic sesame oil， 此日期前最佳為2021年10月6日，以及Organic toasted sesame oil，此日期前最佳是2021年10月9日。兩款產品都是每樽500毫升，進口商 Awesome Foods Limited。<br />\n<br />\n中心發言人說，接獲歐洲聯盟委員會食品和飼料快速預警系統通報，指產品被驗出含有可能致癌的環氧乙烷，正進行回收。中心得悉事件後，聯絡進口商跟進，初步調查發現曾進口部分受影響產品，已按中心指示將產品下架及停售，並展開回收。查詢回收事宜，可於辦公時間致電進口商熱線 3956 9759。<br />\n<br />\n發言人呼籲市民如購入受影響產品，應停止食用。業界如持有有關產品，應停止使用或出售。中心會就事件通知業界，並繼續跟進和採取適當行動。"},{"pid":"cf27a95d3153dd0ea6b841938b792aefb957bdd7","tid":2320110,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"支那製仲毒啦"},{"pid":"f4abe2912162369bc5d648f5b77aabc32062d41d","tid":2320110,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"乜嘢毒都關意粉國事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc033073945c5c275cfd6b9fe5aee2579549deeb","tid":2320110,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf27a95d3153dd0ea6b841938b792aefb957bdd7","tid":2320110,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:09:43.000Z","msg":"支那製仲毒啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:20:11.000Z","msg":"做乜9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0172d257bf3a8f8e014fa47d3699715c3d5040","tid":2320110,"uid":124134,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"啲梅林午餐肉夠話毒到仆街啦<br />\n<br />\n咪又係繼續賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42bcd4ace7cda613974fd68c3522369bbefc86d","tid":2320110,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"下次輪到日本食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847577949616205c64c21f0493a69cddd55dda8b","tid":2320110,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T15:59:38.000Z","msg":"唯有中囯國食物係世界一等純潔"},{"pid":"b756b4c37604c3cb0e8f187e156340ce40e04f9d","tid":2320110,"uid":170335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:00:34.000Z","msg":"芝麻油是蘑菇的"},{"pid":"325cf89110aa841a83462231c7818d791e45588d","tid":2320110,"uid":184261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T16:03:41.000Z","msg":"佢有冇屌過支那啲毒奶粉"},{"pid":"d22ec67c83e9004540253be98007703d3ab5833d","tid":2320110,"uid":34557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"咁芝麻仁呢？"},{"pid":"c8d07075115a203dcb39332264fba0027f6a3d1c","tid":2320110,"uid":268516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T18:02:18.000Z","msg":"芝麻油沒有磨菇"}]}